      "note": "long title",
      "abstract": "To amend sections 109.71, 109.77, 2935.01, 3501.05, 3501.055, 3503.02, 3503.14, 3503.21, 3503.33, 3517.14, 3517.15, and 3517.16 and to enact sections 111.50, 3503.34, and 3503.35 of the Revised Code to make changes to the Election Law regarding voter registration, voter roll maintenance, and enforcement and to name portions of this act the Interstate Voter Assistance Act."
    }
